			<h2 class="topheading"><span class="nfsubhead">Plant Community Classification for Alpine Vegetation on the Beaverhead National Forest, Montana</span><br />PRODUCTIVITY/MANAGEMENT AND SOIL EXCERPTS</h2>
			<p class="note">[Excerpted from: Cooper, Stephen V.; Lesica, Peter; Page-Dumroese, Deborah. Rev. 1997. Plant Community Classification for Alpine Vegetation on the Beaverhead National Forest, Montana. Gen. Tech. Rep. INT-362. Ogden, UT: U.S. Department of Agriculture, Forest Service, Intermountain Research Station. 61 p.]</p>
